# Install uv   <<-- based on Connor's XL training course

WINDOWS:
1. powershell -ExeecutionPolicy ByPass -c "irm https://astral.sh/uv/install.psl | iex"
2. open a new powershell window
3. uv venv --seed
4. uv pip install jupyterlab xlwings openpyxl
5. launch Jupyterlab by executing:   uv run jupyter lab

MACOS:
1. curl -LsSf https://astral.sh/uv/install.sh | sh
2. open a new terminal window
3. uv venv --seed
4. uv pip intsall jupyterlab xlwings openpyxl
5. launch jupyterlab by executing: uv run jupyter lab
